      <title>根據天空新聞報道，黑石將提高對 Hipgnosis 的收購報價</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/blackstone-make-improved-bid-hipgnosis-sky-news-reports-2024-04-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根據天空新聞週日報道，私募股權巨頭 Blackstone 正準備對 Hipgnosis Songs Fund 提出更高的出價，該基金擁有夏奇拉 (Shakira) 和 Blondie 等藝術家的音樂版權。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/blackstone-make-improved-bid-hipgnosis-sky-news-reports-2024-04-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 14:52:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
